claim.claim-text:
6. An apparatus for manufacturing a barrier layer of semiconductor device comprising: 
a reaction chamber; 
a heating unit arranged in the reaction chamber for supporting and heating a semiconductor substrate; 
a microwave generating unit for generating microwave; 
a nitrogen radical generating unit for generating nitrogen radicals by treating nitrogen gas with the microwave; and 
a nitrogen radical injecting unit arranged opposite to the heating unit in the reaction chamber with a predetermined distance for injecting the nitrogen radicals to the semiconductor substrate.
